TextEng: Tell me where he is or me kill you!
Text: 어디 있는지 말해, 안 그러면 죽여!

TextEng: Tell me where he is or I will kill you!
Text: 어디 있는지 말해, 안 그러면 나 죽여!

TextEng: I want to find him. I can't promise he'll be safe.
Text: 난 그를 찾고 싶다. 다만 안전을 보장하진 못해.

TextEng: If you help me find him, I will spare his life.
Text: 그를 찾는 걸 도와주면, 목숨은 살려주지.

TextEng: Idiot! He was playing with people's lives!
Text: 멍청이가! 사람들의 생명을 가지고 놀고 있군!

TextEng: Lord Nasher? Why would he come?
Why he think Nasher come here?
He play with lives like toys!
This game not so funny to Vengaul's men, I bets.
Text: 이 장난, 벵골의 부하들한텐 웃기지도 않았겠지.

TextEng: Help me find, and me spare him.
Me want find him, but me not promise he be okay.
Text: 그를 찾고 싶지만, 무사하단 보장은 못 해.

TextEng: Calm down. I'm not going to hurt you.
Me not going to hurt yous.
And I don't know you. Should I care?
Text: 난 너도 몰라. 내가 왜 신경 써야 해?

TextEng: Me not know you too. Why me care?
Text: 나도 너 몰라. 왜 내가 신경 써?

TextEng: You'll die if you need to.
You die if me say you die.
I want to ask about you.
Me ask about you.
I want to ask about Vengaul.
Me ask about Vengaul.
What do you know about the auction?
What you know of this auction?
I am acting as a guard under Aribeth and Nasher.
Text: 난 아리베스와 나셰르 영주 아래서 경비대 역할을 하고 있어.

TextEng: Me act as guard under Aribeth and Nasher.
Text: 나 아리베스랑 나셰르 영주 밑에서 경비해.

TextEng: That is none of your business.
That my business, lady, not yours.
Text: 그건 내 일이야, 아가씨. 네 일 아냐.

TextEng: Perhaps I'm here to kill you. Perhaps I haven't decided yet.
Text: 아마 널 죽이러 왔을지도. 아직 결정은 안 했지만.

TextEng: Maybe me here to kill you. Maybe me not decide yet.
Text: 아마 너 죽이러 왔어. 아직 못 정했을 뿐.

TextEng: Why were you imprisoned here?
Why you trapped here?
Goodbye.
Why have the Bloodsailors mutinied?
Text: 핏빛 항해자들은 왜 반란을 일으킨 거지?

TextEng: Why Bloodsailors not follow anymore?
Text: 핏빛 항해자 왜 말 안 들어?

TextEng: Where is Vengaul Bloodsail now?
Where Vengaul now?
Back to my previous questions.
We go back to other questions?
Is there one in particular who is guiding this revolt?
There someone leading the traitor sailors?
Where is Callik?
Where Callik now?
What creature do you mean?
What creature you mean?
This game of his would not have pleased his Bloodsailors.
Text: 놈이 벌인 이 장난을 핏빛 항해자 부하들이 좋아할 리 없지.
